OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy start with showers or
OL,6,Flonger spells of rain. Then
OL,7,Fbrightening up from the west with a
OL,8,Ffew passing showers. Windy with strong
OL,9,Fto gale west or southwesterly winds,
OL,10,Foccasionally severe gale across Orkney
OL,11,Fat first.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FRain will spread from the
OL,14,Fwest this evening. Then the rest of
OL,15,Fthe night will see spells of rain,
OL,16,Fbecoming persistent and occasionally
OL,17,Fheavy later. Fresh to strong
OL,18,Fsouthwesterly winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
