OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FRain, heavy at times, will
OL,6,Fclear from the west in the morning.
OL,7,FThen becoming brighter with showers.
OL,8,FFresh southwesterly winds. Cold.
OL,9,
OL,10,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FCold
OL,11,Fwith bright spells and showers on
OL,12,FFriday and Saturday. Rain spreading
OL,13,Feast on Sunday followed by a few
OL,14,Fshowers.
